To install gpx2survex:

1. Install OPAM (e.g. "apt-get install opam") and m4

2. opam switch 4.06.0

3. eval $(opam config env)

4. opam install xmlm core

5. git clone https://github.com/mshinwell/gpx2survex

6. cd gpx2survex

7. dune build gpx2survex.exe

The gpx2survex.exe executable will be found in the "_build/default"
directory.